Vinland Trail

The game where you are Leif Eriksson and everyone dies of scurvy.

Installation:
Just download the contents of the appropriate binary folder, and run the executable. Under Linux, you will need to have the following libraries installed:
 - SDL 1.2
 - SDL_image
 - SDL_mixer
 - SDL_ttf

Compiling from source:
Use g++ or something vaguely compatible. Have development versions of the libraries listed above. Project files for Code::Blocks are included, if you use that IDE.

